#

Arugula and Parmesan Salad

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthyVegetarian

Description

A refreshing and peppery salad topped with nutty Parmesan, perfect for a quick meal or side.

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, shaved
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
